<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 11. Distribution of Pimpla spp. in Uruguay A P. albomarginata Cameron, 1886 B P. caerulea Brulle, 1846 C P. cyanipennis Brulle, 1846 D P. golbachi (Porter, 1970) E P. perssoni Gauld, 1991 F P. patirrufa nom. nov. G P. semirufa Brulle, 1846 H P. tomyris Schrottky, 1902. Gray area = Rocha Department. Red circle = previous record. Blue circle = new record." , "Figure 4. Pimpla cyanipennis Brulle, 1846 (Syntype, sex?) A habitus, lateral view B face, frontal view C mesosoma, dorsal view. Figures by Christophe Herve, MNHN." , "Figure 3. Pimpla cyanipennis Brulle, 1846 (Syntype, ♀) A habitus, lateral view B face, frontal view C mesosoma and part of metasoma, dorsolateral view. Figures by Christophe Herve, MNHN." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/492353" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/492346" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/492345" .

